Critical.Note: "Now called Hedophyllum nigripes (J.Agardh) Starko, S.C.Lindstrom & Martone in the local area (H. bongardiana is a NW Pacific species).  This species has gone by numerous other names in the local flora: Laminaria groenlandica, Saccharina groenlandica, Saccharina nigripes, Saccharina subsimplex--they are all the same thing!” (Sandra Lindstrom, pers. comm. 2023)
“All species formerly called Platythamnion are now recognized as species of Pterothamnion.” (Sandra Lindstrom, pers. comm. 2023)
"Most species previously identified as Porphyra in the local area are now species of Pyropia.” (Sandra Lindstrom, pers. comm. 2023)
note: genomics data resolves only to Rhizosolenia setigera
